{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"115692-betam-tilik-betam-tinish","title":"በጣም ትልቅ! በጣም ትንሽ! ","description":"ሻኑ አሚ እንዳትሸከማት በጣም ትልቅ ነች፡፡ ትምህርት ቤት ብቻዋን ለመሄድ ግን በጣም ትንሽ ነች፡፡ ይህን ተረት ብቻሽን ለማንበብ በጣም ትንሽ ትሆኛለሽ? ወይንስ ሌላ ሰው ጮክ ብሎ እንዳያነብልሽ በጣም ትልቅ ነሽ? ክፈችውና አረጋግጪ! ","language":"Amharic","langCode":"am","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Mezemir Girma"],"illustrators":["Lavanya Karthik"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Ras Abebe Aregay Library","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/115692-betam-tilik-betam-tinish"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42852/size3/0a1060a113ec19cf656ea8d7ef5b0ad9.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42852/size6/0a1060a113ec19cf656ea8d7ef5b0ad9.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42853/size6/70fd0452aa6c927e53d76aa9fb3f4ffc.jpg","text":"ኤሚ ‹‹አንቺን ማንሳት አልችልም፣ ሻን!›› አለች ፡፡\n \n‹‹በጣም   ትልቅ   ነሽ!››","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42854/size6/fc8e07ddde1f569112ef4235e88c71fd.jpg","text":"‹‹ሻኑ ወደ ትምህርት ቤት ብቻሽን መሄድ አትችዪም!›› አለ አቡ፡፡\n \n \n‹‹በጣም  ትንሽ  ነሽ!››","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42855/size6/a26479a6b4ec64005cc22f1749c54a41.jpg","text":"አባባ ‹‹በሕፃኑ አልጋ ላይ መተኛት አትችዪም!›› አለ፡፡\n \n \n‹‹በጣም   ትልቅ   ነሽ!››","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42856/size6/0a0aa02709c207420750b383dd405ace.jpg","text":"አባባ ‹‹ህፃኑን ወደ ፓርኩ መውሰድ አትችዪም!›› አለ፡፡\n \n \n‹‹በጣም ትንሽ   ነሽ!››","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42857/size6/8e306b49594a4a1a1f6c9257e3ba6c31.jpg","text":"ሻኑ ግራ ተጋባች፡፡\nበጣም  ትልቅ!  በጣም ትንሽ!\n \n \nእንዴት በጣም   ትልቅም    በጣም ትንሽም መሆን ትችላለች?","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42858/size6/7073e8462a8a47966202a5fd001b4c11.jpg","text":"የድሮዋን\nሐምራዊ ቀሚስ ለመልበስ በጣም  ትልቅ\nሆናለች፡፡\n \nምድጃው ጋ ዶሴዎችን ለመሥራት በጣም   ትንሽ   ነች፡፡","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42859/size6/21750c3d9a8ed4ca2fce6dfcc3b28c9f.jpg","text":"አባባ\nጀርባ ላይ ለመውጣት በጣም ትልቅ?\n \n \nህፃኑን ለመሸከም በጣም ትንሽ?","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42860/size6/d1e415210fa781719eba663fe762dad9.jpg","text":"‹‹ታዲያ ለምን ይሆን ልከኛ የምሆነው?››\n                                              በማለት\nሻኑ ተገረመች፡፡","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42861/size6/3b099162b2374757bd97fd8040c13e4d.jpg","text":"አሚ ፈገግ እያለች ‹‹ለምን፣ ወደ ትልቅ ትምህርት\nቤት ለመሄድ ዕድሜሽ ደርሷል፡፡››","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42862/size6/3318453c75b535782d8922b62fd31b28.jpg","text":"‹‹\nለእንኮኮ ግን ትንሽ ነሽ›› አለ\nአቡ፡፡","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42863/size6/f1ab7d3d16aba804b07f37f183bd8c12.jpg","text":"‹‹\nጠዋት ጠዋት እኔን ለእግር ጉዞ ለመውሰድ\nደርሰሻል›› አለ አባባ፡፡","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42864/size6/caa5be72b11457da8c4e8b59ee0f0530.jpg","text":"‹‹\nእኔ ተረት እንድነግርሽ አሁንም ትንሽ\nነሽ›› አለ አባባ፡፡","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/42865/size6/c3972c18aa973834eca492ae8b92a1d9.jpg","text":"‹‹እናም ሁልጊዜ፣ ሁልጊዜ ትክክለኛውን መጠን ትሆኛለሽ፡፡…\n \nለዚህ!›› ይሉና ሁሉም በፍቅር እቅፍ ያደርጓታል፡፡","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":13,"words":137}}